            "title": "黑期夜期齊低水逾130點 重磅港股ADR普遍跌逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時13分跌119點或0.45%，報26357點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報26325點，較香港上日現貨收市低162點或0.61%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣593.2元，較上日香港收市低7.81元或1.3%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣158.3元，較上日香港收市低1.39元或0.87%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣96元，較上日香港收市低1.3元或1.34%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣110.7元，較上日香港收市低1.73元或1.54%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣35.1元，較上日香港收市低0.38元或1.09%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣128.7元，較上日香港收市高0.28元或0.22%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣82.1元，較上日香港收市低0.77元或0.92%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣421.5元，較上日香港收市低5.54元或1.3%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣68.3元，較上日香港收市低0.72元或1.04%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣7.7元，較上日香港收市低0.04元或0.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指期貨夜市收報26341點，跌121點，較上日恒指收市26487點，低水147點。科指期貨夜市收報5638點，較上日科指收市低水45點；國指期貨夜市收報9044點，較上日國指收市低水51點。</p>\n</div>",
